A little midweek inspiration with this evocative moment on Mallorca by @voyage_provocateur of dinner time at El Olivo @belmondlaresidencia 
Wishing everyone a great day! 
Be sure to look at this in Reels to get the full effect and be sure to tag a friend who would love to see this 😍
Gorgeous reel by @voyage_provocateur
PS the music is by @maxrichtermusic  but for some reason Instagram isn’t recognizing it or allowing me to edit the attribution.
